            {
               "text": "### Images from University Johannesburg\n\nThese images are copyright for University Johannesburg and allowed to be used according to the license determined by them.\n\nTo visualize all images, use the left and right arrows on the slide below.",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p><div class=\"htSlides\"><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">1 / 1</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgShona\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgShona', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Photos of a Shona kitchen. In the top left, we see a photo of the kitchen with the door closed. In the top right, we see the back of the kitchen. In the bottom section, there are images of the interior of the structure. These photos were taken by Brian Z. Muratu (<htcite0>) and are being used under the terms defined by the University of Johannesburg, which shared the dissertation under the <a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/\" target=\"_blank\">Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0)</a> license.</div><div class=\"htSlideRefs\"><b>Related content:</b><ul><li>Hands and music (<a href=\"index.html?page=math_games\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('math_games','html', '', false); return false;\">Mathematical Games</a>)</li><li>Cooking with numbers (Universe)</li><li>Limiting (Universe)</li><li>There is something else (Universe)</li><li>Together we are strong (Universe)</li></ul></div></div><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-left htSlidePrev\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(-1);\"></i><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-right htSlideNext\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(1);\"></i></div></p>",
